# Media Framing Analysis with NLP

This project analyzes how Donald Trump is represented in news coverage mentioning Jeffrey Epstein.

Data sources
- New York Times API
- Fox News website

Methods
- Named Entity Recognition
- Dependency Parsing
- Sentiment Analysis
- Keyword in Context (KWIC)
- Narrative Frame Detection
- Network Analysis

Libraries
- spaCy
- pandas
- seaborn
- NetworkX
- TextBlob
